main event: An observer reported seeing a pulsating starlike object over Belleview, Florida on clear nights.
interesting points: The object is described as pulsating or flashing on and off as it moved over the horizon., The observer claims to see this object every clear night after sundown., This sighting has been reported multiple times by the same observer., The conclusion states that the sighting is astronomical in nature., The object appeared very low and disappeared over the horizon during descent.
witness description: an observer who has reported this sighting multiple times
